# Auto-fix with archguardian

When the user asks to fix findings:

1. Preview with `npx archguardian fix --dry-run --format json`
2. Show what will change (file, line, description)
3. Ask for confirmation
4. Apply with `npx archguardian fix`
5. Re-scan to verify fixes: `npx archguardian scan --format json`
6. Report before/after comparison

Supported fixes: unused import removal, naming convention renames.
